BXD Data

Read count

BXDcount<-read.table("ATAC_SEQ_BXD.Counts.txt",header=T,row.names=1)

Filter low counts

#meanBXDcount<-apply(BXDcount,1,mean)
#BXDcount<-BXDcount[meanBXDcount>10,]

Normalization

Get lines factors

lines<-colnames(BXDcount)
lines[grep("BXD90",lines)]<-'BXD90'
lines[grep("B6D2F1",lines)]<-'B6D2F1'
lines[grep("D2B6F1",lines)]<-'B2B6F1'
lines[grep("BL6",lines)]<-'BL6'
lines[grep("BXD55",lines)]<-'BXD55'
lines[grep("BXD89",lines)]<-'BXD89'
lines[grep("BXD87",lines)]<-'BXD87'
lines[grep("DBA2",lines)]<-'DBA2'
BXDnorm <- DGEList(counts=BXDcount)
BXDnorm <- calcNormFactors(BXDnorm,method="TMM")
design <- model.matrix(~0+lines)
BXDnorm<-estimateDisp(BXDnorm,design)

color<-rainbow(8)[as.factor(lines)]
plotMDS(BXDnorm,col=color)

Contrast with C57BL6

fit <- glmFit(BXDnorm, design)
my.contrasts <- makeContrasts("linesBL6-linesBXD55","linesBL6-linesBXD87","linesBL6-linesBXD89","linesBL6-linesBXD90", levels=design)
BXD55
lrt.BL6vs55 <- glmLRT(fit, contrast=my.contrasts[,"linesBL6-linesBXD55"])
FDR <- p.adjust(lrt.BL6vs55$table$PValue, method="BH")
lrt.BL6vs55$table$FDR<-FDR
BL6vs55.table<-lrt.BL6vs55$table[lrt.BL6vs55$table$FDR<=0.05,]
BL6vs55.table<-BL6vs55.table[order(abs(BL6vs55.table$logFC),decreasing=T),]
head(BL6vs55.table)

Time Course Data

Read count

TCcount<-read.table("ATAC_SEQ_TimeCourse.Counts.txt",header=T,row.names=1)

Filter low counts

#meanTCcount<-apply(TCcount,1,mean)
#TCcount<-TCcount[meanTCcount>10,]

Normalization

Get Time and Condition factor

Cond<-rep("NSD",ncol(TCcount))
Cond[grep("S",colnames(TCcount))]<-"SD"

Time<-c()
for (i in colnames(TCcount)){
  Time<-c(Time,str_extract(i,"[T|ZT|J]\\d+"))
}

TimeCond<-paste(Time,Cond,sep="_")
TCnorm <- DGEList(counts=TCcount)
TCnorm <- calcNormFactors(TCnorm,method="TMM")
design <- model.matrix(~0+TimeCond)
TCnorm<-estimateDisp(TCnorm,design)

par(mfrow=c(1,3))
color<-rainbow(length(unique(TimeCond)))[as.factor(TimeCond)]
plotMDS(TCnorm,col=color)

color<-rainbow(length(unique(Cond)))[as.factor(Cond)]
plotMDS(TCnorm,col=color)

color<-rainbow(length(unique(Time)))[as.factor(Time)]
plotMDS(TCnorm,col=color)

plotBCV(TCnorm)

Contrast

fit <- glmFit(TCnorm, design)
my.contrasts <- makeContrasts("TimeCondT12_SD-TimeCondT12_NSD","TimeCondT6_SD-TimeCondT6_NSD","TimeCondT3_SD-TimeCondT3_NSD","TimeCondT54_SD-TimeCondT6_NSD","TimeCondT48_SD-TimeCondT0_NSD","TimeCondT18_SD-TimeCondT18_NSD","TimeCondT24_SD-TimeCondT0_NSD","TimeCondJ70_SD-TimeCondT0_NSD","TimeCondJ76_SD-TimeCondT6_NSD", levels=design)

DE Figure

par(mfrow=c(3,3))
dt <- decideTestsDGE(lrt.3v3,adjust.method="BH", p.value=0.05)
status<-dt[,1]
status2<-status
status2[status==0]<-(-1)
status2[status==(-1)]<-0
plotMD(lrt.3v3,status=status2,main="ZT3 SD/NSD",cex=.7)
